{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1539710/extras/Banner_Title_AlwaysBlasting.png?t=1720715826\" /><br>The smooth movement combined with arcade-y gunplay is what makes shooting zombies and robots super fun. Go for a high streak with a shotgun, wallrun and grapple to traverse the map quickly, dash and double jump to dodge enemy projectiles, and/or use a windblast to clear out a group of zombies.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1539710/extras/DeadBlitZ_EnemyGrapple_2.gif?t=1720715826\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1539710/extras/Banner_Title_AlwaysMoving.png?t=1720715826\" /><br>Once on the battlefield, enemies will be relentless and never stop. Your objective is to secure zones and then escape through a portal. However, with each zone secured, enemies grow stronger and faster. So keep moving and keep shooting.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1539710/extras/DeadBlitZ_DoubleJump_to_SlideKill_2.gif?t=1720715826\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1539710/extras/Banner_Title_LevelUp.png?t=1720715826\" /><br>To counter enemies becoming too powerful, aim for kills, high streaks, and/or secure zones to fill up the upgrade bar. Once filled, you are granted an upgrade point. Use upgrade points at any time during a run to enhance your base abilities and also receive a MAX HEALTH, DAMAGE, and/or AMMO CAPACITY bonus multiplier.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1539710/extras/DeadBlitZ_Upgrade_2.gif?t=1720715826\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Tutorial","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1539710/a1